{"title":"第三幕 冰原的故事","date":"2020-07-18T03:45:04.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 18, 2020","L":"07/18/2020","MM-DD":"07-18"},"author":"WardZhou","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/powder-snow-496875_640.webp","link":"2020/07/18/StoryOfIceField","comments":true,"tags":["Paddy","诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.496Z","content":"<p><em>柔板</em><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p>雪落冰原<br>\n留下的脚印转眼<br>\n又被抚平<br>\n面包屑也<br>\n不见了踪迹</p>\n<p>雪停了<br>\n西风带来一场绵雨<br>\n融化了雪<br>\n又凝成冰霜<br>\n再次被雪覆盖</p>\n<p>等东风失势<br>\n再迎雪雨之舞<br>\n消失的脚印将这<br>\n一幕幕<br>\n悉数重唱</p>\n","prev":{"title":"各花 TheFlower","link":"2020/07/26/TheFlower"},"next":{"title":"Cat!Cat!Cat!","link":"2020/07/12/CatCatCat"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/07/18/StoryOfIceField/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"WardZhou","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"}}